descriptionHtml:
first upload of a complete whiterun retexture mod. more textures will be added.
check darooz.com for updates as mods always gets uploaded there first. this is just to show that the skyrim/oblivion retexturing break is over.

check my previously uploaded whiterun files\' screenshots to get a hunch what it is that im offering
quality resolutions etc

any questions or requests of any kind
dont hesitate to ask

1.2 changelog: Stonewall normalmap made more \"bumpier\" by dusing the layer blur overlays method in photoshop over the crazybump generated normal map. i also increased brightness and contrast on the alpha channel to make the texture\'s highlights reflect more light and  the shadows less light which make it look more realistic
author: Darooz
